These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, chinese, nigerian
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, light-blue, blue, apricot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff, dannemann, bongani
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, scientist, nurse, security-guard
 1. the scientist is the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the chinese is the person who likes blue##1
 3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the security-guard##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the italian is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 6. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
 7. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 8. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
10. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
11. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality          | nigerian     | italian   | dutch | chinese |
| Color   | light-blue | chestnut    | apricot   | blue    |
| Cigar           | dannemann       | bongani   | aristoff   | fonseca     |
| Job     | scientist       | fisherman | security-guard  | nurse      |

