.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, dunhill, ritmeester
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, domino, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, marigold, rose
House: victorian, gothic-revival, townhouse, craftsman
 1. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who growsrose is the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing bridge is between the person playing poker and the blend-smoker##2
 8. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
 9. the person who growsdahlia is the person playing poker##1
10. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
11. the victorian house is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar      | blend       | bolivar | ritmeester     | dunhill     |
| Game   | snooker      | bridge       | poker | domino |
| Flower           | marigold       | rose    | dahlia     | zinnia         |
| House     | craftsman | townhouse     | victorian     | gothic-revival       |

