.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, coach, fisherman, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, tennis, basketball
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, mah-jongg, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, azalea, daisy
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 4. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
 5. the coach is on the left of the police-officer##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is between the person playing whist and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 9. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the police-officer##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | lawyer    | fisherman      | coach   | police-officer |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | cycling | basketball  |
| Game   | billiard   | mah-jongg         | backgammon  | whist  |
| Flower           | azalea      | iris          | daisy | lily  |

