 2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 5. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 6. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is between the havana-smoker and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
10. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
11. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
13. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5

.:: Answer ::.
