 3. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
 4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 6. the mexican is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the polish##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
 9. the polish is the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person traveling to paris is in an even position##4
11. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
