.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-6::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, mah-jongg, go
City: berlin, new-york, hamburg, liverpool
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, aconite, dahlia
4 different pets are kept: horse, frog, chinchilla, rabbit
 1. the person who growsaconite is between the person playing monopoly and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
 3. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 9. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
12. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
13. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Game      | monopoly             | snooker       | go    | mah-jongg       |
| City          | new-york             | hamburg      | liverpool     | berlin    |
| Flower           | dahlia | aconite | daisy     | zinnia |
| Pet   | frog           | chinchilla | rabbit | horse |

