.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
City: new-york, edinburgh, san-francisco, nizza
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine, colombian, dutch
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, ritmeester, siglo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, nizza-polo, badminton, volleyball
 1. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 2. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person traveling to new-york and the siglo-smoker##2
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 6. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 8. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
12. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| City      | nizza   | new-york | edinburgh   | san-francisco          |
| Nationality          | argentine    | dutch        | colombian     | egyptian          |
| Cigar           | game | ritmeester        | bluemaster | siglo |
| Sport   | volleyball    | tennis     | badminton      | nizza-polo        |

