.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, cycling, parkour
City: miami, marseilles, berlin, liverpool
There 4 different types of food: lemon, peach, carrot, asparagus
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, fish, pony
 1. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
 4. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to berlin and the person eating asparagus##2
 6. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to berlin is the person eating peach##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
12. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | cycling   | parkour      | sailing | ice-hockey     |
| City           | liverpool   | miami  | marseilles        | berlin |
| Food   | lemon     | asparagus     | carrot      | peach   |
| Pet     | dog | fish | pony          | turtle     |

