.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
House: ranch-style, wooden, palace, gothic-revival
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, motorbike, ship, taxi
City: paris, new-york, marseilles, san-francisco
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lavender, turquise, fuchsia
 1. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
 4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
 7. the person driving the ship is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
11. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
12. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| House          | ranch-style | palace  | gothic-revival    | wooden       |
| Transport           | motorbike  | taxi | ship | train  |
| City   | new-york    | marseilles   | san-francisco  | paris     |
| Color   | fuchsia      | turquise    | lavender        | brown |

 